# Token Studio — Referensi & Workflow

## Intinya

- **`single/tokens.json`** = source design (sync Figma, single-file, **di-commit**)
- **`sets/`** = derived multi-file (generate via `sync:split` setelah pull)
- Referensi di **`sets/`** tanpa prefix set; di **`single/tokens.json`** dengan prefix set (untuk Style Dictionary)

## Workflow Free tier

```
Figma push → single/tokens.json → git pull → sync:split → sets/ → build
```

```bash
pnpm --filter @fatedart/tokens sync:split
pnpm --filter @fatedart/tokens build
```

## Format referensi di `sets/`

| Konteks | Salah | Benar |
|---------|-------|-------|
| Cross-set ke core | `{core.spacing.sm}` | `{spacing.sm}` |
| Cross-set ke semantic | `{semantic.color.action.primary}` | `{color.action.primary}` |
| Cross-set ke typography | `{typography.crv.body-medium.small}` | `{crv.body-medium.small}` |
| Same-set | `{components.button.radius}` | `{button.radius}` |

`sync:split` otomatis menormalisasi prefix setelah split.

## Aturan edit

1. **Desain:** edit di Figma → push `single/tokens.json` → pull → `sync:split`
2. **Engineer (jarang):** edit `sets/` → `sync:merge` → commit `single/tokens.json` → pull di Figma
3. Jangan edit `sets/` manual tanpa sync balik ke `tokens.json`

## Gejala alias rusak

Titik merah di Token Studio = prefix set tersisa di `sets/`. Jalankan `sync:split` atau `fix-cross-set-refs.mjs`.
